(5, 0, 0, 10, 1, NULL, NULL, '', 'https://imgr2.akdgame.com/220x220/games/fruits-match/s512x512.png', NULL, 1, 1, 'Fruits Match', 'fruits-match', '<p>Fruits Match is a match-three game where you collect three matching tiles to clear them. Collect and clear three or more fruit tiles to solve the stage. You may use one additional deck, shuffle, or undo chance per stage. These powerups allow you to add an additional deck slot, shuffle the cards or undo your previous action. Get started today and show the world your mastery of fruit-matching!</p>', NULL, 0, 0, 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/4810e00e5ee74b518728b24626b3bcf6/', '2023-12-20 02:44:21', '2024-06-11 20:11:39'),
(6, 0, 0, 10, 1, NULL, NULL, '', 'https://imgr2.akdgame.com/220x220/games/funny-blade-and-magic/s512x512.png', NULL, 1, 13, 'Funny Blade & Magic', 'funny-blade-and-magic', 'Become a goblin hero betrayed by your uncle and stripped of his legacy in this addictive game. Fight in close combat with a wide arsenal of weapons including swords, axes and hammers. Feel the power of magic as you wield various spells and abilities such as time dilation and teleportation. Get ready for epic battles against unique bosses and enemies with a variety of abilities and tactics. Watch exciting cutscenes that will immerse you in the unique universe of the game.', NULL, 0, 0, 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/9f994d6bf74c4decae5cb4a60f357d93/', '2023-12-20 02:44:21', '2024-06-11 20:11:32'),
(7, 1, 0, 10, 1, NULL, NULL, '', 'https://imgr2.akdgame.com/220x220/games/oil-race-3d/s512x512.png', NULL, 1, 13, 'Oil Race 3D', 'oil-race-3d', 'You can progress towards wealth by collecting oil barrels in the Oil Race 3D game. Fill the vehicles on the platform with oil barrels and continue on your way, passing the opponents with them. You can unlock new hats with the coins you earn Come on and show them who\'s rich!', NULL, 0, 0, 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/f49b1222fccf4ce29856a04de9d2cbb8/', '2023-12-20 02:44:21', '2025-11-10 03:01:00'),
(8, 0, 0, 10, 1, NULL, NULL, '', 'https://imgr2.akdgame.com/220x220/games/traffic-rider-moto-bike-racing/s512x512.png', NULL, 1, 14, 'Traffic Rider Moto Bike Racing', 'traffic-rider-moto-bike-racing', 'If you are bored of playing typical bike driving games and want some rust and challenges. Then this new “Highway Traffic Bike Rider Game” is specially developed for you. Traffic bike riding is a tough thing to do, unless you love to ride a bike on highway roads and have traffic from both sides, you should be a pro stuntman to do so. Get your sports bike on the road and be aware of traffic all around. Challenge yourself and rush into the highway! Race, Dodge, Overtake, and Go FAST!', NULL, 0, 0, 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/3ae409f702f64fab98743afbfdf211a1/', '2023-12-20 02:44:21', '2023-12-10 18:43:35'),
