(34, 0, 0, 10, 1, NULL, '-7-thXQ_ugY', '', 'https://img.gamepix.com/games/mahjong-connect-spooky/cover/mahjong-connect-spooky.png?w=320', NULL, 1, 1009, 'Mahjong Connect Spooky', 'mahjong-connect-spooky', '<div>\n <h2>About the Game</h2>\n <p>Enter the eerie world of <strong>Mahjong Connect Spooky</strong>, a captivating twist on the classic tile-matching game. This spooky-themed edition challenges players to strategically connect identical tiles, clearing the board while immersed in a hauntingly beautiful atmosphere. Instead of the traditional Mahjong setup, <strong>Mahjong Connect Spooky</strong> requires you to connect matching tiles with paths that have no more than two 90-degree bends. This adds an extra layer of strategic depth to the gameplay, demanding careful planning and sharp observation skills.</p>\n <p>Developed by GamePix, <strong>Mahjong Connect Spooky</strong> is accessible directly through your browser. The game is perfect for players of all skill levels, from casual puzzlers to seasoned Mahjong veterans. The atmospheric visuals, combined with the engaging gameplay, make <strong>Mahjong Connect Spooky</strong> a truly captivating experience. Prepare to lose yourself in a world of spooky fun as you test your memory and strategic thinking.</p>\n \n <h2>How to Play</h2>\n <p>Playing <strong>Mahjong Connect Spooky</strong> is simple to learn but challenging to master. Here\'s a breakdown of the gameplay:</p>\n <ol>\n <li><strong>Identify Matching Tiles:</strong> Scan the board for two identical tiles.</li>\n <li><strong>Connect the Tiles:</strong> Click on the first tile, then click on the second matching tile.  The game will automatically create a path to connect them.</li>\n <li><strong>Path Restrictions:</strong> The connecting path <u>cannot</u> have more than two 90-degree bends. If a valid path exists, the tiles will disappear.</li>\n <li><strong>Clear the Board:</strong> Your goal is to eliminate all the tiles from the board before the timer runs