(123, 0, 0, 10, 1, NULL, NULL, '', 'https://imgr2.akdgame.com/220x220/games/garden-tales-4/s512x512.png', NULL, 1, 7, 'Garden Tales 4', 'garden-tales-4', '<p>Garden Tales 4 blossoms as a popular match-3 puzzle game. Players swap adjacent elements to create matches of three or more identical fruits, flowers, or vegetables. The game\'s objective is to complete level-specific goals, such as clearing a certain number of items or reaching a target score. Strategic planning and clever combos are key to success in this vibrant and engaging title.</p>\r\n<p>Are you ready for a garden adventure? Garden Tales 4 provides hours of relaxing yet stimulating gameplay. Jump into this colorful world and test your puzzle-solving skills, all for free on AkdGame!</p>\r\n<h2 id=\"how-to-play-garden-tales-4-\">How to Play Garden Tales 4?</h2>\r\n<h3 id=\"how-to-control-garden-tales-4-\">How to Control Garden Tales 4?</h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><strong>Mouse:</strong>&nbsp;Use the mouse to select and swap adjacent game elements.</li>\r\n<li><strong>Left Mouse Button:</strong>&nbsp;Click to select an item and then click on an adjacent item to swap them.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h3 id=\"how-do-you-clear-obstacles-\">How Do You Clear Obstacles?</h3>\r\n<p>Obstacles like stones, weeds, and ice blocks stand in your way. Matching items adjacent to these obstacles clears them, allowing you to progress. Focus on eliminating these impediments to open up the board and create more matching opportunities.</p>\r\n<h3 id=\"how-to-make-special-items-\">How to Make Special Items?</h3>\r\n<p>Match more than three items to create special items like bombs, rockets, and butterflies. These power-ups can clear entire rows, columns, or clusters of items. Strategically combining special items unleashes devastating chain reactions, helping you achieve level goals faster.</p>\r\n<h3 id=\"what-does-the-shovel-item-do-\">What Does The Shovel Item Do?</h3>\r\n<p>The shovel is a handy tool. This item allows you to remove any single item on the board. Use it wisely to get rid of troublesome pieces that block potential matches or to complete level-specific objectives.</p>\r\n<h3 id=\"what-kind-of-prizes-and-rewards-await-\">What Kind of Prizes and Rewards Await?</h3>\r\n<p>As you complete levels, you earn stars and other rewards. These can unlock new levels, boosters, and customization options. Keep playing to collect them all and enhance your Garden Tales 4 experience.</p>\r\n<h3 id=\"what-challenges-do-ice-blocks-present-\">What Challenges Do Ice Blocks Present?</h3>\r\n<p>Ice blocks freeze items, preventing them from being swapped. To clear ice blocks, you need to match items adjacent to them multiple times. Prioritize removing ice blocks to free up frozen items and expand your matching possibilities.</p>\r\n<h3 id=\"are-there-any-games-like-garden-tales-4-on-AkdGame-\">Are There any Games Like Garden Tales 4 on AkdGame?</h3>\r\n<p>If you\'re looking for an alternative match-3 experience, there\'s a list of games available to play for free on AkdGame:</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><a href=\"https://akdgame.com/g/reversi\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Reversi</a></li>\r\n<li><a href=\"https://akdgame.com/g/daily-sudoku\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Daily Sudoku</a></li>\r\n<li><a href=\"https://akdgame.com/g/mahjong-solitaire\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Mahjong Solitaire</a></li>\r\n<li><a href=\"https://akdgame.com/g/hangman\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Hangman</a></li>\r\n<li><a href=\"https://akdgame.com/g/word-search\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Word Search</a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h2 id=\"who-developed-garden-tales-4-\">Who Developed Garden Tales 4?</h2>\r\n<p>Garden Tales 4 is developed by Softgames, a game developer known for creating engaging and accessible online games.</p>\r\n<h3 id=\"what-is-the-release-date-of-garden-tales-4-\">What is the Release Date of Garden Tales 4?</h3>\r\n<p>Garden Tales 4 was released on August 15, 2023. It continues the popular Garden Tales series.</p>\r\n<h3 id=\"what-are-the-best-games-from-this-developer-\">What are The Best Games From This Developer?</h3>\r\n<p>Other popular games from Softgames include:</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Bubble Shooter HD 4</li>\r\n<li>Garden Tales</li>\r\n<li>Solitaire Story - Tripeaks 4</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>Garden Tales 4 offers a delightful and addictive match-3 experience. Its vibrant visuals and strategic gameplay make it a perfect choice for puzzle enthusiasts. Dive in and cultivate your own garden of fun for free on AkdGame today!</p>', NULL, 1, 0, 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/e27f5122f42b44239f4bb2a90feeed06/', '2023-12-20 02:44:21', '2025-07-03 18:19:22'),
