(183, 0, 0, 10, 1, NULL, NULL, '', 'https://imgr2.akdgame.com/220x220/games/11x11-bloxx/s512x512.png', NULL, 1, 90, '11X11 Bloxx', '11x11-bloxx', '11+11 Bloxx,\" also known as \"11x11 Blocks,\" is a captivating block-puzzle game that distinguishes itself by employing an 11x11 game board instead of the traditional 10x10 grid. In this game, your objective is to strategically position multi-colored polyomino shapes onto the board to accumulate coins and points by forming rows and columns comprised of precisely 11 blocks.', NULL, 0, 0, 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/3a7e200ffd0544a1bf9fb028b349eb0d/', '2023-12-20 02:44:21', '2024-05-17 02:07:40'),
