(195, 0, 0, 10, 1, NULL, NULL, '', 'https://imgr2.akdgame.com/220x220/games/blockfit-puzzler/s512x512.png', NULL, 1, 7, 'Blockfit Puzzler', 'blockfit-puzzler', 'Step into a world of challenging puzzles and intriguing perspectives with BlockFit Puzzler! Strategically align the blocks in the upper layer to match perfectly with the patterns in the lower layer in an isometric perspective. With levels ranging from 3x3 to 5x5, you\'ll need logical reasoning and sharp visual skills to conquer. Embark on this block-aligning journey, solve captivating puzzles, and overcome challenges in pursuit of perfection!', NULL, 0, 0, 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/74ac12fb37804b29869691447c46c1b3/', '2023-12-20 02:44:21', '2024-05-17 02:07:43'),
