(197, 0, 0, 10, 1, NULL, NULL, '', 'https://imgr2.akdgame.com/220x220/games/ragdoll-down/s512x512.png', NULL, 1, 9, 'Ragdoll Down', 'ragdoll-down', 'An exciting arcade game in which players are given a unique opportunity to inflict maximum damage to ragdoll in various extreme conditions. You\'ll have to use a variety of objects and environments to accomplish this goal. Waiting for you are: ✅ Ragdoll physics. ✅ Shop with items ✅ Vivid graphics', NULL, 0, 0, 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/7df53cd5678342459d05cef570a1551c/', '2023-12-20 02:44:21', '2023-12-10 18:43:35'),
(199, 0, 0, 10, 1, NULL, NULL, '', 'https://imgr2.akdgame.com/220x220/games/penalty-shooters-3/s200x200-1727774310.png', NULL, 1, 431, 'Penalty Shooters', 'penalty-shooters', '<p>\"Penalty Shooters\" is a hugely popular free online game that puts you right in the heart of a penalty shootout. The game genre is sports simulation. Your task involves scoring goals as the striker and saving them as the goalkeeper. To win, you\'ll need sharp reflexes, precise timing, and a bit of strategy to outwit your opponent. One prominent feature is the ability to customize your team and compete in various tournaments.</p>\r\n<p>In short, \"Penalty Shooters\" offers an engaging and competitive experience for soccer fans. Jump into playing this game on AkdGame.</p>\r\n<h2 id=\"how-to-play-penalty-shooters-\">How to Play Penalty Shooters?</h2>\r\n<h3 id=\"how-to-control-penalty-shooters-\">How to Control Penalty Shooters?</h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><strong>Mouse:</strong>&nbsp;Aim and shoot as a striker; move gloves as a goalkeeper.</li>\r\n<li><strong>Click:</strong>&nbsp;Perform actions.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h3 id=\"how-do-you-aim-your-shots-accurately-\">How Do You Aim Your Shots Accurately?</h3>\r\n<p>To aim effectively, pay close attention to the power bar and the target area. Click when the power bar is at the desired level for shot strength. Also, anticipate the goalie\'s movements to place your shot strategically. Faking one way and shooting the other can throw them off.</p>\r\n<h3 id=\"how-can-you-save-penalties-as-the-goalkeeper-\">How Can You Save Penalties as the Goalkeeper?</h3>\r\n<p>As a goalkeeper, watch the striker\'s movements closely. Try to anticipate which direction they will shoot by observing their body language. Move your gloves quickly to intercept the ball. Timing is crucial!</p>\r\n<h3 id=\"what-are-the-prizes-and-rewards-\">What are the Prizes and Rewards?</h3>\r\n<p>Winning matches and tournaments in \"Penalty Shooters\" earns you in-game currency and trophies. You can use the currency to upgrade your team\'s skills and unlock new customization options. The better you perform, the greater the rewards.</p>\r\n<h3 id=\"what-are-the-obstacles-\">What are The Obstacles?</h3>\r\n<p>One of the main obstacles is facing increasingly skilled opponents as you advance through the tournaments. Their shots become harder to predict, and their goalkeeping becomes more adept. Adapting your strategy is essential to overcome these challenges.</p>\r\n<h3 id=\"how-to-choose-best-team\">How to Choose Best Team</h3>\r\n<p>When selecting your team, consider their skill levels in shooting accuracy, power, and goalkeeping ability. Look for a balanced team with strengths in both attacking and defending. Experiment with different formations to find what works best for your play style.</p>\r\n<h3 id=\"are-there-any-games-like-penalty-shooters-on-AkdGame-\">Are There any Games Like Penalty Shooters on AkdGame?</h3>\r\n<p>If you\'re looking for an alternative \"Penalty Shooters\". There\'s a list of games available to play for free on AkdGame:</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><strong><a href=\"https://akdgame.com/g/penalty-rivals\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Penalty Rivals</a></strong></li>\r\n<li style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><strong><a href=\"https://akdgame.com/g/rugby-rush\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Rugby Rush</a></strong></li>\r\n<li style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><strong><a href=\"https://akdgame.com/g/kix-dream-soccer\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">KiX Dream Soccer</a></strong></li>\r\n<li style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><strong><a href=\"https://akdgame.com/g/free-kick-shooter\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Free Kick Shooter</a></strong></li>\r\n<li style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><strong><a href=\"https://akdgame.com/g/football-3d\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Football 3D</a></strong></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h2 id=\"who-developed-penalty-shooters-\">Who Developed Penalty Shooters?</h2>\r\n<p>\"Penalty Shooters\" is developed by FlashFooty, known for creating various online sports games with simple, accessible gameplay.</p>\r\n<h3 id=\"what-is-the-release-date-of-penalty-shooters-\">What is the Release Date of Penalty Shooters?</h3>\r\n<p>\"Penalty Shooters\" was initially released in 2012. The game has remained a popular choice for fans of penalty shootout games.</p>\r\n<h3 id=\"what-are-the-best-games-from-this-developer-\">What are The Best Games From This Developer?</h3>\r\n<p>Other popular games from FlashFooty include:</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Free Kick League</li>\r\n<li>Goalkeeper Premier</li>\r\n<li>Penalty Fever</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>\"Penalty Shooters\" provides a simple yet addictive experience for soccer enthusiasts, making it a great option for casual players. Test your skills and compete in thrilling penalty shootouts, play for free on AkdGame today!</p>', '/199/thumbnail.3x3.h264.mp4', 1, 0, 'https://h5.akdgame.com/game-assets/17276799812528/index.html', '2023-12-20 02:44:21', '2025-08-13 09:58:13'),
