(203, 0, 0, 10, 1, NULL, NULL, '', 'https://imgr2.akdgame.com/220x220/games/parkour-world/s512x512.png', NULL, 1, 995, 'Parkour World', 'parkour-world', '<p dir=\"ltr\">Welcome to Parkour World, an exciting game that challenges you to jump, climb, and navigate floating obstacles as you race towards the sky. In this thrilling adventure, each level gets tougher, pushing your focus and reflexes to their limits. Prepare to soar to new heights and explore a vast world filled with opportunities to show off your parkour skills. As you progress, you&rsquo;ll encounter various hurdles that test your abilities. Get ready to rise up and conquer the challenges of Parkour World!</p>\r\n<h2 dir=\"ltr\">How To Control Parkour World?</h2>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li dir=\"ltr\" aria-level=\"1\">\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">Run: Shift</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li dir=\"ltr\" aria-level=\"1\">\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">Jump: Space</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li dir=\"ltr\" aria-level=\"1\">\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">Walk around: WASD/ Arrow keys</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h2 dir=\"ltr\">How To Play Parkour World?</h2>\r\n<h3 dir=\"ltr\">Mastering the Controls</h3>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">In Parkour World, you\'ll use the keyboard to control your character&rsquo;s movements. Press the spacebar to jump over obstacles and climb higher. Timing your jumps is crucial, especially as the levels get harder. Make sure to practice your jumps to ensure you can land on floating platforms and avoid falling.</p>\r\n<h3 dir=\"ltr\">Navigating Obstacles</h3>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">As you progress through each level, you\'ll encounter various floating obstacles that you must climb or jump over. Pay close attention to the layout of each level and look for the best path to take. Use your reflexes to dodge hazards and keep moving upward. The more you practice, the better you&rsquo;ll become at navigating the challenges in Parkour World!</p>\r\n<h2 dir=\"ltr\">What Are Some Good Tips And Tricks For Parkour World?</h2>\r\n<h3 dir=\"ltr\">Practice Your Jumps</h3>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Timing is essential in Parkour World. Make sure to practice your jumps on various obstacles to get a feel for how far and high you can jump. If you miss a platform, you may fall and have to restart. Try to observe the distances and adjust your timing accordingly to improve your accuracy.</p>\r\n<h3 dir=\"ltr\">Explore the Levels</h3>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Take time to explore each level before making a big jump. Look for the best routes and patterns in the floating obstacles. Some paths may be less obvious but can lead to easier navigation or even hidden areas that reward you with bonus points or achievements.</p>\r\n<h3 dir=\"ltr\">Stay Focused and Calm</h3>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">As the levels progress, the challenges become more intense. It&rsquo;s easy to feel rushed, but staying calm will help you react better to obstacles. Keep your focus on your character\'s movements and anticipate upcoming jumps. This will improve your overall performance and help you conquer tougher levels.</p>\r\n<h2 dir=\"ltr\">Are There Any Games Like Parkour World?</h2>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li dir=\"ltr\" aria-level=\"1\">\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">Free Running 2</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li dir=\"ltr\" aria-level=\"1\">\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">Vector</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li dir=\"ltr\" aria-level=\"1\">\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">Parkour Simulator 3D</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li dir=\"ltr\" aria-level=\"1\">\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">Mirrors Edge Catalyst</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li dir=\"ltr\" aria-level=\"1\">\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">Ninja Dash Run</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>', '/203/thumbnail.3x3.h264.mp4', 1, 0, 'https://h5.akdgame.com/game-assets/17269880182216/index.html', '2023-12-20 02:44:21', '2025-07-21 18:35:46'),
