(209, 0, 0, 10, 1, NULL, NULL, '', 'https://imgr2.akdgame.com/220x220/games/cookie-crush-3-1/s512x512.png', NULL, 1, 7, 'Cookie Crush 3', 'cookie-crush-3-1', '<p>Cookie Crush 3 is a popular online puzzle game where players match colorful cookies to clear the board and advance through levels. This engaging match-3 game requires strategic thinking and quick reflexes. The goal is to swap adjacent cookies to create lines of three or more of the same type, causing them to disappear. Mastering special cookie combinations is the key to racking up high scores.</p>\r\n<p>In short, Cookie Crush 3 offers hours of sweet, addictive fun with its vibrant graphics and challenging gameplay. Ready for a sugar rush? Play Cookie Crush 3 for free on AkdGame!</p>\r\n<h2 id=\"how-to-play-cookie-crush-3-\">How to Play Cookie Crush 3?</h2>\r\n<h3 id=\"how-to-control-cookie-crush-3-\">How to Control Cookie Crush 3?</h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><strong>Mouse:</strong>&nbsp;Use the mouse to click and drag cookies to swap their positions.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h3 id=\"how-do-you-make-special-cookies-\">How Do You Make Special Cookies?</h3>\r\n<p>Creating special cookies is key to clearing levels quickly. Match four cookies in a row to create a striped cookie, which clears an entire row or column when matched. Combine five cookies in an L or T shape to form a wrapped cookie, which explodes when matched, clearing the surrounding area. Matching five cookies in a line creates a rainbow cookie, which eliminates all cookies of a single color when swapped with another cookie.</p>\r\n<h3 id=\"what-happens-when-you-level-up-\">What Happens When You Level Up?</h3>\r\n<p>As you progress through Cookie Crush 3, the levels become increasingly challenging. New obstacles and goals are introduced, keeping the gameplay fresh and engaging. Leveling up unlocks new areas, boosters, and challenges. The higher the level, the more strategic you need to be to achieve the level goals.</p>\r\n<h3 id=\"what-is-the-chocolate-block-\">What is the Chocolate Block?</h3>\r\n<p>Chocolate blocks are a common obstacle in Cookie Crush 3. They spread across the board with each turn if not cleared. Match cookies next to the chocolate blocks to remove them. Prioritize clearing chocolate blocks to prevent them from taking over the board and hindering your progress.</p>\r\n<h3 id=\"what-rewards-can-you-earn-\">What Rewards Can You Earn?</h3>\r\n<p>Cookie Crush 3 offers various rewards for completing levels and achieving specific goals. You can earn boosters, extra lives, and in-game currency. These rewards can help you overcome difficult levels and progress further in the game.</p>\r\n<h3 id=\"how-do-you-use-boosters-\">How Do You Use Boosters?</h3>\r\n<p>Boosters are special items that can help you clear levels more easily. The hammer booster, for example, removes a single cookie from the board. The shuffle booster rearranges the cookies, while the row or column clear boosters eliminate entire rows or columns. Use boosters strategically to overcome obstacles and reach your goals.</p>\r\n<h3 id=\"what-are-the-level-objectives-\">What are the Level Objectives?</h3>\r\n<p>Each level in Cookie Crush 3 has specific objectives that you must complete to advance. These objectives can include clearing a certain number of cookies, achieving a specific score, or removing obstacles like jelly or chocolate blocks. Pay close attention to the level objectives and plan your moves accordingly to maximize your chances of success.</p>\r\n<h3 id=\"are-there-any-games-like-cookie-crush-3-on-AkdGame-\">Are There any Games Like Cookie Crush 3 on AkdGame?</h3>\r\n<p>If you\'re looking for an alternative to Cookie Crush 3, there\'s a list of games available to play for free on AkdGame:</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Candy Match 2</li>\r\n<li>Jewel Burst</li>\r\n<li>Skydom Reforged</li>\r\n<li>Blocks Puzzle Zoo</li>\r\n<li>Sea Merge</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h2 id=\"who-developed-cookie-crush-3-\">Who Developed Cookie Crush 3?</h2>\r\n<p>Cookie Crush 3 is developed by Clever Apps Pte. Ltd, a game developer known for creating engaging and addictive puzzle games.</p>\r\n<h3 id=\"what-is-the-release-date-of-cookie-crush-3-\">What is the Release Date of Cookie Crush 3?</h3>\r\n<p>Cookie Crush 3 was released on March 21, 2018. Since then, it has gained immense popularity among puzzle game enthusiasts worldwide.</p>\r\n<h3 id=\"what-are-the-best-games-from-this-developer-\">What are The Best Games From This Developer?</h3>\r\n<p>Other popular games from Clever Apps Pte. Ltd include:</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Candy Match</li>\r\n<li>Christmas Crush</li>\r\n<li>Sweet Sugar</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>Cookie Crush 3 offers a delightful and addictive puzzle experience that\'s easy to pick up but challenging to master. Dive in and satisfy your sweet tooth for free on AkdGame today!</p>', NULL, 1, 0, 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/9e019e5c38a74fb9b8893662795e06b2/', '2023-12-20 02:44:21', '2025-08-15 05:32:04'),
