(1, 'About', 'about', '<p><em>Welcome to PlayVio.io — Where Boredom Goes to Die</em></p><p>Ever found yourself mindlessly clicking through tabs, hoping something fun will magically appear?&nbsp;</p><p>Yeah, we’ve been there too — and that’s exactly why PlayVio.io exists.</p><p>We’re not just another browser game site thrown into the internet void. We’re your escape hatch, your pixel-packed playground, your 2 AM “just one more game” destination. PlayVio.io is where bite-sized fun meets endless entertainment, all wrapped up in a slick, no-install, play-right-now kind of vibe.</p><p>But hey — before you lose yourself in a clicker frenzy or dodge enemies like a pro, let’s take a little trip down memory lane.</p><h2>🎮 The Story Behind the Screen</h2><p>It all started in a dorm room… okay, maybe not. More like a very messy desk somewhere between deadlines and existential crisis.</p><p>The idea was simple:</p><p>“Let’s create a place where people can play awesome browser games without the fluff, the ads overload, or the ‘Download This Plugin’ drama.”</p><p>We were a small crew of developers, designers, caffeine enthusiasts, and gamers (obviously) who felt like online gaming had gotten either too complicated or too boring. You either had to download giant files, sit through a dozen ads, or play games that looked like they hadn’t aged a day since 2005.</p><p>So we thought: What if we made it ridiculously easy to have fun online again?<br> And boom — PlayVio.io was born.</p><h2>🕹️ What We Do (Besides Playing Too Much)</h2><p>We curate, test, and hand-pick the best browser games the web has to offer.<br> Not just games — we’re talking:</p><p><strong></strong></p><ul><li><p><strong>Addictive clicker games<br></strong></p></li><li><p><strong>Fast-paced arcade madness<br></strong></p></li><li><p><strong>Mind-bending puzzle challenges<br></strong></p></li><li><p><strong>Chill-out idle games<br></strong></p></li><li><p><strong>Multiplayer mayhem<br></strong></p></li><li><p><strong>And plenty more pixelated goodness<br><br></strong></p></li></ul><p><strong>We don’t just throw every game at the wall to see what sticks. Nope.<br> Every game you see on PlayVio.io has passed our “Is this worth skipping lunch over?” test. (That’s our official metric — don’t @ us.)</strong></p><h2><strong>🔥 Why We’re Different (In a Good Way)</strong></h2><p><strong>You’ve probably seen a dozen game sites that all look the same, right?<br> Cluttered homepages, low-quality games, shady popups, and that one music loop that never ends.<br> Yeah, not our style.</strong></p><p><strong>Here’s what makes PlayVio.io pop:</strong></p><ul><li><p><strong>No logins. No installs. Just play.<br></strong></p></li><li><p><strong>Mobile-friendly &amp; lag-free (even on your grandma’s phone)<br></strong></p></li><li><p><strong>Super clean UI — like “I can find what I want without rage clicking” clean<br></strong></p></li><li><p><strong>New games every week, sometimes daily<br></strong></p></li><li><p><strong>Minimal ads, max gameplay — because your time is too precious to waste<br><br></strong></p></li></ul><p><strong>We believe browser gaming should be snackable, sharable, and seriously fun.<br> It’s like TikTok, but for games… and with a lot less dancing.</strong></p><h2><strong>🤝 Built by Gamers, for Gamers (and the Gamer-Curious)</strong></h2><p><strong>Whether you’re a die-hard gamer who eats leaderboard scores for breakfast or someone just trying to kill time between Zoom calls — PlayVio.io has something for you.</strong></p><p><strong>We obsess over the small things:</strong></p><ul><li><p><strong>Is the clicker game satisfying?<br></strong></p></li><li><p><strong>Does that puzzle game make your brain smile?<br></strong></p></li><li><p><strong>Is the UI clean enough to game one-handed while holding a burrito?<br><br></strong></p></li></ul><p><strong>Basically, we sweat the pixels so you don’t have to.</strong></p><h2><strong>🌐 Our Mission: Pure, Unfiltered Fun</strong></h2><p><strong>Let’s be real — life can be a lot. Deadlines, drama, doomscrolling… sometimes you just need a break.</strong></p><p><strong>So our mission is pretty straightforward: Deliver joy through tiny moments of play.<br> Whether that’s a 5-minute burst or a 3-hour binge — we’re here for it.</strong></p><p><strong>PlayVio.io is your secret productivity killer.&nbsp; (We won’t tell your boss.)</strong></p><h2><strong>✨ The Tech Magic Behind It All</strong></h2><p><strong>Okay, tech nerds, this one’s for you.</strong></p><p><strong>PlayVio.io runs on a lean, optimized, cloud-powered backend with lightning-fast delivery. We’ve crafted a game loader that makes sure your play starts now, not in 8 seconds. Our front-end? Designed to be buttery-smooth on any screen size — whether you’re tapping on a tablet or smashing keys on a mechanical keyboard.</strong></p><p><strong>And yes, we geek out on game performance. Because lag ruins lives. Period.</strong></p><h2><strong>💌 The Humans Behind PlayVio</strong></h2><p><strong>We’re not some faceless corp in a glass building. We’re a lean indie team with dirty coffee mugs, half-charged laptops, and an obsession with perfecting fun.</strong></p><p><strong>Here’s a sneak peek at our crew:</strong></p><ul><li><p><strong>Max – The Game Curator with 3,000 hours on Steam (and counting)<br></strong></p></li><li><p><strong>Luna – UX designer, cat mom, and queen of color palettes<br></strong></p></li><li><p><strong>Jay – Code wizard who once built a game in a Taco Bell<br></strong></p></li><li><p><strong>Rico – Our meme lord &amp; community guy (who replies way too fast)<br><br></strong></p></li></ul><p><strong>We’re building PlayVio.io not just as a site, but as a community of fun-seekers.<br> We want you to feel like you just walked into a digital arcade that never closes.</strong></p><h2><strong>🚀 What’s Next?</strong></h2><p><strong>Oh, we’re just getting started.</strong></p><p><strong>Coming soon:</strong></p><ul><li><p><strong>User profiles and achievement badges<br></strong></p></li><li><p><strong>Global leaderboards (finally flex those scores)<br></strong></p></li><li><p><strong>Game reviews written by players, not robots<br></strong></p></li><li><p><strong>Community tournaments with real prizes (bragging rights + swag)<br></strong></p></li><li><p><strong>Creator support — so indie devs can share their awesome games with the world<br><br></strong></p></li></ul><p><strong>Our roadmap is filled with pixels, passion, and a lot of caffeine-fueled ideas.</strong></p><h2><strong>🎉 Let’s Keep It Playful</strong></h2><p><strong>So yeah — that’s us.<br> We’re PlayVio.io. We’re a little quirky, a little nerdy, and very, very into games.</strong></p><p><strong>Whether you’re here for a quick dopamine hit or a night-long button-mashing adventure, we’re glad you landed on our turf. Bookmark us. Share us. Obsess over your high score. And if you ever feel like suggesting a game, roasting our UI, or just saying “hey,” we’re only one click away.</strong></p><p><strong>Thanks for playing with us.<br> Stay curious. Stay playful. Stay Vio.</strong></p><h2><strong>👾 Got Questions? Let’s Talk!</strong></h2><p><strong>We’re real people who read every message (yes, even the weird ones).<br> If you’ve got feedback, partnership ideas, or want to feature your game — hit us up on the Contact Us page.</strong></p><p><strong>Or email us at: contact@playvio.io</strong></p><p><strong>Let’s build something awesome together.<br> Game on. 🎮</strong></p><p></p>				', '2025-11-17 03:01:41', '2025-11-17 03:01:41'),
(2, 'Developer Welcome 🎮', 'developer', '<p><span>Got Games? We’ve Got Players. Let’s Team Up.</span></p><p><span>Hey devs — we see you.&nbsp;</span></p><p><span>Burning the midnight oil. Squashing bugs. Celebrating small wins like \"finally fixed the jump physics.\" Whether you\'re a one-person game wizard or a full-blown studio with beanbags and espresso machines, welcome to </span><span>PlayVio.io</span><span> — your new favorite publishing playground.</span></p><p><span>We’re not just a platform.&nbsp;</span></p><p><span>We’re a growing hub for browser gamers across the globe who are </span><span>hungry</span><span> for fun, fast, and creative games that don\'t need to be downloaded or installed.</span></p><p><span>If you\'ve built something cool — something </span><span>clicky</span><span>, </span><span>quirky</span><span>, </span><span>competitive</span><span>, or downright </span><span>chaotic</span><span> — let’s get it in front of the crowd.</span></p><h2><span>🚀 Why Partner with PlayVio.io?</span></h2><p><span>We keep it simple. We keep it fun. We bring the players.</span></p><p><span>Here’s what’s in it for you:</span></p><h3><span>1. Instant Reach</span></h3><p><span>Get your game in front of </span><span>thousands of active players</span><span> who visit PlayVio.io daily. No installs. No gatekeeping. Just pure exposure.</span></p><h3><span>2. 100% Credit to You</span></h3><p><span>Your name, your studio, your links — all front and center. We give proper credit, backlinks, and shoutouts in every listing.</span></p><h3><span>3. Zero Cost. Zero Hassle.</span></h3><p><span>No sign-up fees, no confusing portals. Just email us your game, and we’ll take it from there. Simple is our favorite feature.</span></p><h3><span>4. Feedback &amp; Playtesting</span></h3><p><span>Our community LOVES trying new stuff. Get early reactions, bug reports, and gameplay feedback — organically.</span></p><h3><span>5. Cross-Promotion Opportunities</span></h3><p><span>Want your game featured on our homepage, social media, or newsletters? Let’s talk highlights, events, and maybe even </span><span>high score bounties</span><span>.</span></p><h2><span>📦 What We Accept</span></h2><p><span>We’re open to </span><span>HTML5 browser-based games</span><span> across all genres:</span></p><p><strong></strong></p><ul><li><p><strong><span>Action &amp; Clickers</span></strong></p> </li><li><p><strong><span>Puzzle &amp; Brain Teasers</span></strong></p> </li><li><p><strong><span>Platformers</span></strong></p> </li><li><p><strong><span>Racing &amp; Sports</span></strong></p> </li><li><p><strong><span>Casual &amp; Idle</span></strong></p> </li><li><p><strong><span>Multiplayer (WebRTC, WebSockets welcome)</span></strong></p> </li></ul><p><strong><span>Whether your game was built with </span><span>Construct</span><span>, </span><span>Unity WebGL</span><span>, </span><span>Phaser</span><span>, </span><span>Godot</span><span>, or your own home-brewed engine — if it plays great in a browser, we want to see it.</span></strong></p><h2><strong><span>🧩 Developer Submission Checklist</span></strong></h2><p><strong><span>If you’re ready to submit your game for PlayVio.io, here’s what we need from you:</span></strong></p><ul><li><p><strong><span>A playable HTML5/WebGL build (hosted or zipped)</span></strong></p> </li><li><p><strong><span>Game title and short description</span></strong></p> </li><li><p><strong><span>Cover image or thumbnail (512x384 or 512x512 preferred)</span></strong></p> </li><li><p><strong><span>Name/Studio credit + website or portfolio link</span></strong></p> </li><li><p><strong><span>Instructions or controls</span></strong></p> </li><li><p><strong><span>Any monetization guidelines (if applicable)</span><span><br><br></span></strong></p> </li></ul><p><strong><span>💌 </span><span>Email it to:</span><span> devs@playvio.io</span><span><br></span><span> 📎 Subject Line: </span><span>Game Submission – [Your Game Name]</span></strong></p><h2><strong><span>💡 Looking for Feedback?</span></strong></h2><p><strong><span>We love helping early-stage games find their footing. If you’re testing a beta version or need community feedback — we can mark it as “In Development” with a feedback form link or Discord invite.</span></strong></p><p><strong><span>Our players love playing — and talking about what they’re playing. Use the momentum to squash bugs, polish gameplay, or even build your fanbase.</span></strong></p><h2><strong><span>🔐 Your Game, Your Rights</span></strong></h2><p><strong><span>Let’s be super clear:</span></strong></p><p><strong><span>You own everything you send us. </span><span>&nbsp;We’re just here to showcase your work and help it reach more eyes (and mouse clicks).</span></strong></p><p><strong><span>We don’t:</span></strong></p><ul><li><p><strong><span>Modify your game without permission</span></strong></p> </li><li><p><strong><span>Claim ownership of your code, assets, or ideas</span></strong></p> </li><li><p><strong><span>Sell or relicense your work behind your back</span></strong></p> </li></ul><p><strong><span>Need your game removed later? No problem. Just shoot us an email and we’ll take it down within 24 hours.</span></strong></p><p><strong><span>We’re developers too — we get it.</span></strong></p><h2><strong><span>📢 Sponsored Spots &amp; Monetization</span></strong></h2><p><strong><span>Want to </span><span>promote your game</span><span> even further? We’ve got:</span></strong></p><ul><li><p><strong><span>Homepage features</span><span><br></span></strong></p> </li><li><p><strong><span>Sponsored game slots</span><span><br></span></strong></p> </li><li><p><strong><span>Leaderboard shoutouts</span><span><br></span></strong></p> </li><li><p><strong><span>Newsletter plugs</span><span><br><br></span></strong></p> </li></ul><p><strong><span>If you\'re a studio or indie dev with a launch coming up, we can offer flexible promotion plans based on your goals and budget. Let us know what you’re planning — we love celebrating game launches!</span></strong></p><p><strong><span>We’re also open to discussing </span><span>revenue-share models</span><span>, </span><span>pre-roll ads</span><span>, or </span><span>brand sponsorships</span><span> inside featured games.</span></strong></p><p><strong><span>📩 Hit us up at devs@playvio.io to talk biz.</span></strong></p><h2><strong><span>🛠️ Game Hosting Options</span></strong></h2><p><strong><span>You can host the game yourself and send us an iframe link, OR send us a .zip of your HTML5 build — and we’ll host it on our blazing-fast servers.</span></strong></p><p><strong><span>Just let us know which you prefer. Either way, it’ll load fast and smooth on mobile and desktop.</span></strong></p><p><strong><span>Need help optimizing your WebGL export for browser play? We can point you in the right direction.</span></strong></p><h2><strong><span>🧑‍💻 Indie Devs, This Is Your Playground</span></strong></h2><p><strong><span>PlayVio.io was built by indie creators who knew the struggle of getting visibility.</span><span><br></span><span> We </span><span>want</span><span> to champion small devs, side projects, student games, and experimental builds.</span></strong></p><p><strong><span>Whether you\'re on your 1st or 15th title, your game deserves a shot in front of real players.</span></strong></p><h2><strong><span>💬 Let’s Collaborate</span></strong></h2><p><strong><span>Got a game jam project?</span><span><br><br></span></strong></p><p><strong><span>Want to build a custom PlayVio-themed mini-game for our audience? Thinking of doing a limited-time event, leaderboard challenge, or collab stream?</span></strong></p><p><strong><span>Let’s make something epic together.</span></strong></p><p><strong><span>🎮 Got ideas? We’re just one email away:</span></strong></p><p><strong><span>&nbsp;devs@playvio.io</span></strong></p><h2><strong><span>📣 Final Words (Before We Dive Back Into Debug Mode)</span></strong></h2><p><strong><span>If you’ve got a game and a dream, we’ve got the players and the platform.</span></strong></p><p><strong><span>Submit. Showcase. Shine.</span></strong></p><p><strong><span>Let’s turn clicks into fans, bugs into polish, and browser games into internet gold.</span></strong></p><p><strong><span>Catch you in the high scores,</span><span><br></span><span> </span><span>The PlayVio Dev Team</span></strong></p><p></p>			', '2025-11-17 03:17:24', '2025-11-17 03:17:24'),
(3, 'Privacy', 'Privacy Policy', '	<p><span>Effective Date:</span><span> October 7, 2025</span></p><p><span>Website: </span><a href=\"\"><span>PlayVio.io</span></a></p><p><span>Operator:</span><span> PlayVio Media (“PlayVio”, “we”, “our”, or “us”)</span></p><p><span>Your privacy matters. At PlayVio.io, we’re committed to safeguarding your personal information and ensuring transparency about how your data is collected, used, and protected when you visit or interact with our website.</span></p><p><span>This Privacy Policy explains what data we collect, how we use it, your rights under applicable laws (including </span><span>GDPR</span><span>, </span><span>CCPA</span><span>, and </span><span>COPPA</span><span>), and how to contact us with any concerns.</span></p><p><span>1. Scope of This Policy</span></p><p><span>This Privacy Policy applies to all visitors and users of PlayVio.io, including those in the </span><span>United States</span><span>, </span><span>European Union</span><span>, </span><span>United Kingdom</span><span>, and other applicable regions. By accessing the site, you consent to the practices described herein.</span></p><p><span>If you do not agree with any part of this policy, please discontinue your use of the website.</span></p><h2><span>2. Information We Collect</span></h2><p><span>We do not require registration or personal data to access games. However, we may collect the following categories of data:</span></p><h3><span>2.1 Non-Personal Information (Automatically Collected)</span></h3><p><span>We collect anonymous or aggregated data through cookies and tracking tools, including:</span></p><p><strong></strong></p><ul><li><p><strong><span>IP address (anonymized where possible)</span></strong></p></li><li><p><strong><span>Browser type and version</span><span><br></span></strong></p></li><li><p><strong><span>Device type and operating system</span></strong></p></li><li><p><strong><span>Geographic region (generalized)</span></strong></p></li><li><p><stron