cklace</th>\n        <th>Earrings</th>\n        <th>Bracelet</th>\n        <th>Hair Accessory</th>\n      </tr>\n    </thead>\n    <tbody>\n      <tr>\n        <td>Classic Ball Gown (Red)</td>\n        <td>Diamond Pendant</td>\n        <td>Diamond Studs</td>\n        <td>Silver Chain Bracelet</td>\n        <td>Tiara</td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr>\n        <td>Sleek Mermaid Dress (Blue)</td>\n        <td>Statement Necklace (Silver)</td>\n        <td>Hoop Earrings (Silver)</td>\n        <td>None</td>\n        <td>Hair Clip with Blue Gems</td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr>\n        <td>Flowy A-Line Dress (Pink)</td>\n        <td>Pearl Necklace</td>\n        <td>Pearl Drop Earrings</td>\n        <td>Pearl Bracelet</td>\n        <td>Floral Hair Clip</td>\n      </tr>\n    </tbody>\n  </table>\n\n  <h2>Conclusion: Shine Bright at the Party!</h2>\n  <p>By following these tips and using your creativity, you can help Bella become the most shining star at the party in <em>Perfect Prom Dressup</em>. Remember to experiment with different combinations and have fun with the process. Now go out there and create some stunning looks!</p>\n</div>', 'https://cdn.jovani.com/wp-content/uploads/D5711-1.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=MWXRhYD2wxE', 'MWXRhYD2wxE', 0, 5, 2, 'published', 'Perfect Prom Dressup: Dominate the Dance Floor with These Winning Outfits & Strategies!', 'Chia sẻ mẹo và hướng dẫn chơi Perfect Prom Dressup chi tiết nhất.', 'Perfect Prom Dressup, Dressup Games, Fashion Games, Game Guide, Styling Tips', '2025-10-22 16:05:47', '2025-10-22 09:05:47', '2025-10-22 09:05:47'),
(7, 0, 'Space Donut Domination: Your Guide to Conquering Cosmic Pastries!', 'space-donut-domination-your-guide-to-conquering-cosmic-pastries', 'space-donut', 'Space Donut Domination: Your Guide to Conquering Cosmic Pastries!Space Donut, the addictive casual space shooter, might seem simple at first glance, but mastering it requires strategy and finesse. Thi...', '<div><h2>Space Donut Domination: Your Guide to Conquering Cosmic Pastries!</h2><p>Space Donut, the addictive casual space shooter, might seem simple at first glance, but mastering it requires strategy and finesse. This guide will transform you from a rookie space baker to a cosmic donut demolisher!</p><h2>Understanding the Basics: Astronauts and Alien Bosses</h2><p>In Space Donut, you control a lone donut on a mission to… well, obliterate everything! Your primary targets are:</p><ul><li><b>Astronauts:</b> These are your bread-and-butter enemies. They appear in waves and are relatively easy to defeat, but their sheer numbers can be overwhelming.</li><li><b>Alien Bosses:</b> These are the big kahunas! Each boss has unique attack patterns and weaknesses. Learn them or perish!</li></ul><h2>Mastering Donut Maneuvers</h2><p>Your donut isn\'t just for show! Mastering movement and shooting is crucial.</p><ul><li><b>Precise Movement:</b> Use the controls to dodge enemy fire and position yourself strategically.</li><li><b>Power-Ups:</b> Collect power-ups to enhance your donut\'s abilities! Speed boosts, rapid fire, and shields can turn the tide of battle.</li></ul><h2>Astronaut Annihilation Strategies</h2><p>Dealing with the astronaut hordes requires a multi-pronged approach:</p><ol><li><b>Prioritize Weaker Enemies:</b> Focus fire on the astronauts with lower health to thin the ranks quickly.</li><li><b>Use Environment to Your Advantage:</b> If available, use asteroids or other obstacles as temporary cover.</li><li><b>Donut Circles:</b> Consider doing donut circles to get better at avoiding shots and collecting more power-ups.</li></ol><h2>Alien Boss Beatdowns: A Step-by-Step Guide</h2><p>Each boss requires a different strategy, but here\'s a general approach:</p><table><thead><tr><th>Step</th><th>Action</th><th>Rationale</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>1</td><td>Observe Attack Patterns</td><td>Identify predictable attacks to exploit.</td></tr><tr><td>2</td><td>Identify Weak Points</td><td>Target areas where the boss takes increased damage.</td></tr><tr><td>3</td><td>Utilize Power-Ups</td><td>Save power-ups for when you need them most, such as during a boss\'s powerful attacks.</td></tr><tr><td>4</td><td>Maintain Distance</td><td>Stay far enough away to react to attacks, but close enough to deal damage.</td></tr></tbody></table><h2>Advanced Tips and Tricks</h2><ul><li><b>Practice Makes Perfect:</b> Don\'t get discouraged if you struggle at first. Keep playing, and you\'ll gradually improve.</li><li><b>Experiment with Different Power-Up Combinations:</b> See what works best for your play style.</li><li><b>Watch Gameplay Videos:</b> Learn from experienced players.</li></ul><h2>Conclusion: From Pastry Pushover to Cosmic Conqueror</h2><p>Space Donut is more than just a casual game; it\'s a test of skill and strategy. By following this guide, you\'ll be well on your way to becoming a Space Donut master. Now go forth and conquer those cosmic pastries!</p></div>', 'https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/mario/images/3/3f/SMBW_Bowser_Artwork.png/revision/latest?cb=20230910142646', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=s5AU-MGEGbo', 's5AU-MGEGbo', 0, 5, 1, 'published', 'Space Donut Domination: Your Guide to Conquering Cosmic Pastries!', 'Chia sẻ mẹo và hướng dẫn chơi Space Donut chi tiết nhất.', 'Space Donut, Space Shooter, Game Guide, Strategy, Tips and Tricks', '2025-10-22 16:06:40', '2025-10-22 09:06:40', '2025-10-22 09:06:40'),
(9, 0, 'Survive the Undead Rising: A Portal of Doom Strategy Guide', 'survive-the-undead-rising-a-portal-of-doom-strategy-guide', 'portal-of-doom-undead-rising', 'Portal of Doom Undead Rising: Mastering the Space Station NightmarePortal of Doom Undead Rising plunges you into a terrifying sci-fi horror scenario. You\'ve answered a distress call from a space stati...', '<div><h2>Portal of Doom Undead Rising: Mastering the Space Station Nightmare</h2><p>Portal of Doom Undead Rising plunges you into a terrifying sci-fi horror scenario. You\'ve answered a distress call from a space station, a hub for clandestine experiments gone horribly wrong. This guide provides essential strategies to survive the undead onslaught and uncover the truth behind the portal.</p><h2>Understanding the Threats</h2><p>Before diving in, familiarize yourself with the enemy types. Expect:</p><ul><li><b>Basic Undead:</b> Slow but numerous. Conserve ammo when dealing with hordes.</li><li><b>Armored Undead:</b> Require more firepower. Aim for weak spots (head, exposed joints).</li><li><b>Special Infected (e.g., Spitter, Charger):</b> Possess unique abilities. Prioritize eliminating them quickly.</li><li><b>Boss Encounters:</b> Prepare for challenging fights. Learn their attack patterns and exploit vulnerabilities.</li></ul><h2>Essential Survival Tips</h2><p>These tips will significantly improve your chances of survival:</p><ul><li><b>Conserve Ammo:</b> Ammo is scarce. Use melee attacks when safe.</li><li><b>Scavenge Thoroughly:</b> Search every nook and cranny for supplies (ammo, health packs, key items).</li><li><b>Use the Environment:</b> Utilize choke points and environmental hazards to your advantage.</li><li><b>Upgrade Your Weapons:</b> Prioritize weapon upgrades to increase damage and efficiency.</li><li><b>Listen Carefully:</b> Audio cues can alert you to approaching enemies.</li><li><b>Strategic Retreat:</b> Don\'t be afraid to fall back to a safer location if overwhelmed.</li></ul><h2>Weapon Loadout Recommendations</h2><p>Choosing the right weapon loadout is crucial. Consider these options:</p><table border=\"1\"><tr><th>Weapon</th><th>Strengths</th><th>Weaknesses</th><th>Recommended Use</th></tr><tr><td>Pistol</td><td>Ammo efficient, readily available</td><td>Low damage</td><td>Early game, conserving ammo</td></tr><tr><td>Shotgun</td><td>High damage at close range</td><td>Limited range, slow reload</td><td>Clearing rooms, dealing with hordes</td></tr><tr><td>Assault Rifle</td><td>Versatile, good for medium range</td><td>Ammo consumption</td><td>Engaging enemies at medium range, sustained fire</td></tr><tr><td>Energy Weapon</td><td>High damage, penetrates armor</td><td>Limited ammo, overheating</td><td>Taking down armored enemies and bosses</td></tr></table><h2>Navigating the Space Station</h2><p>The space station is a labyrinthine environment. Pay close attention to:</p><ul><li><b>Map:</b> Use the map to navigate and identify key locations.</li><li><b>Key Codes and Cards:</b> Find key codes and cards to unlock new areas.</li><li><b>Environmental Hazards:</b> Watch out for explosive barrels, electrified floors, and other hazards.</li></ul><h2>Boss Battle Strategies</h2><p>Each boss encounter requires a unique strategy. Here\'s a general approach:</p><ol><li><b>Observe Attack Patterns:</b> Learn the boss\'s attack patterns and telegraphs.</li><li><b>Identify Weak Points:</b> Target the boss\'s weak points for maximum damage.</li><li><b>Utilize Cover:</b> Use cover to avoid taking damage.</li><li><b>Conserve Resources:</b> Manage your ammo and health packs carefully.</li></ol><h2>Unlocking the Secrets of the Portal</h2><p>As you progress, you\'ll uncover the secrets of the portal and the experiments that led to the undead outbreak. Pay attention to:</p><ul><li><b>Audio Logs:</b> Audio logs provide valuable clues about the story.</li><li><b>Documents:</b> Read documents to learn more about the experiments and the scientists involved.</li><li><b>Environmental Storytelling:</b> Observe the environment for clues about what happened on the space station.</li></ul><h2>Conclusion: Embrace the Challenge</h2><p>Portal of Doom Undead Rising is a challenging but rewarding game. By mastering these strategies, you\'ll increase your chances of survival and uncover the secrets of the portal. Good luck, and may you survive the undead rising!</p></div>', 'https://play-lh.googleusercontent.com/kaSBCPWnGyDZeT056tLtP9t20eTsszbPWpYscIQSJwvlv3oSzv8xd5Z0yULMxwOmBME=w526-h296-rw', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Qxs_v4Nf2C8', 'Qxs_v4Nf2C8', 0, 3, 1, 'published', 'Survive the Undead Rising: A Portal of Doom Strategy Guide', 'Chia sẻ mẹo và hướng dẫn chơi Portal Of Doom Undead Rising chi tiết nhất.', 'Portal of Doom Undead Rising, Strategy Guide, Horror Game, Sci-Fi Horror, Undead, Survival Tips', '2025-10-22 16:07:15', '2025-10-22 09:07:15', '2025-10-22 09:07:15'),
(10, 0, 'Mastering Avoid It: The Ultimate Guide to Dodge, Survive, and Conquer!', 'mastering-avoid-it-the-ultimate-guide-to-dodge-survive-and-conquer', 'avoid-it', '\nWelcome, Avoid It Enthusiasts!\nAvoid It, with its deceptively simple art style and intensely addictive gameplay, has captured the hearts of mobile gamers everywhere. But beneath the charming exterior...', '<div>\n<h2>Welcome, Avoid It Enthusiasts!</h2>\n<p>Avoid It, with its deceptively simple art style and intensely addictive gameplay, has captured the hearts of mobile gamers everywhere. But beneath the charming exterior lies a challenging game that demands quick reflexes, strategic thinking, and a healthy dose of patience. This comprehensive guide will provide you with the tips, tricks, and strategies you need to go from novice to master and conquer Avoid It\'s most treacherous obstacles.</p>\n\n<h2>Understanding the Basics</h2>\n<p>The core mechanic of Avoid It is straightforward: use your finger to guide your character and avoid the incoming obstacles. However, mastering this basic movement is key to long-term success. Here\'s a breakdown:</p>\n<ul>\n  <li><b>Precision is Paramount:</b> Don\'t make broad, sweeping movements. Small, controlled adjustments are often more effective.</li>\n  <li><b>Anticipation is Key:</b> Observe the patterns of the obstacles. Predict where they\'re going and plan your movements accordingly.</li>\n  <li><b>Practice Makes Perfect:</b> The more you play, the better you\'ll become at reading the game and reacting quickly.</li>\n</ul>\n\n<h2>Advanced Strategies for Survival</h2>\n<p>Once you\'ve grasped the basics, it\'s time to delve into more advanced techniques:</p>\n\n<h3>1. The Art of the Feint</h3>\n<p>Sometimes, the best way to avoid an obstacle is to trick it. Briefly move towards it, then quickly dodge out of the way as it approaches. This can be particularly effective against obstacles with predictable movement patterns.</p>\n\n<h3>2. Cornering the Market (Literally!)</h3>\n<p>Utilize the corners of the screen to your advantage. They can provide temporary safe havens and allow you to regroup before tackling the next wave of obstacles.</p>\n\n<h3>3. Mastering the Slow-Mo Moment</h3>\n<p>While not always available, some power-ups may provide a slow-motion effect. Use these opportunities wisely to navigate particularly challenging sections.</p>\n\n<h3>4. Prioritize Survival Over High Scores (Early On)</h3>\n<p>In the beginning, focus on simply staying alive. Once you\'ve developed your skills and understanding of the game, you can start pushing for higher scores.</p>\n\n<h2>Analyzing Obstacle Patterns</h2>\n<p>Avoid It features a variety of obstacle types, each with its unique movement pattern. Identifying these patterns is crucial for survival:</p>\n\n<ul>\n  <li><b>Linear Obstacles:</b> Move in straight lines. Focus on precise dodging.</li>\n  <li><b>Rotating Obstacles:</b> Rotate around a central point. Predict their rotation and find gaps to slip through.</li>\n  <li><b>Homing Obstacles:</b> Follow your character. Use feints and quick changes in direction to evade them.</li>\n  <li><b>Combined Obstacles:</b> A mix of different obstacle types. Requires a combination of all the above strategies.</li>\n</ul>\n\n<h2>Practice Drills to Sharpen Your Skills</h2>\n<p>Here are a few practice drills you can use to improve your Avoid It skills:</p>\n\n<ul>\n  <li><b>Obstacle Identification:</b> Focus solely on identifying the types of obstacles that appear.</li>\n  <li><b>Movement Drills:</b> Practice quick, precise movements in a small area.</li>\n  <li><b>Pattern Recognition:</b> Watch replays of your gameplay to identify recurring obstacle patterns.</li>\n</ul>\n\n<h2>Conclusion: Embrace the Challenge and Keep Dodging!</h2>\n<p>Avoid It is a game that rewards persistence and dedication. By mastering the basic mechanics, employing advanced strategies, and practicing regularly, you can conquer even the most challenging obstacles and achieve mastery. So, keep dodging, keep improving, and most importantly, keep having fun!</p>\n</div>', 'https://expcarry.com/image/cache/catalog/blog/World%20of%20Warcraft/manaforge-omega-boss-guide-780x475.png', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=EMNy1EJgPK4', 'EMNy1EJgPK4', 0, 6, 1, 'published', 'Mastering Avoid It: The Ultimate Guide to Dodge, Survive, and Conquer!', 'Chia sẻ mẹo và hướng dẫn chơi Avoid It chi tiết nhất.', 'Avoid It, Mobile Game, Strategy Guide, Tips and Tricks, Gaming Guide', '2025-10-22 16:07:28', '2025-10-22 09:07:28', '2025-10-22 09:07:28'),
(11, 0, 'Armedforces.io Domination: The Ultimate Guide to Victory!', 'armedforcesio-domination-the-ultimate-guide-to-victory', 'armedforces-io', 'Armedforces.io: Gear Up and Dominate!Armedforces.io throws you into intense firefights across diverse maps, offering a variety of game modes for every play style. Whether you\'re a seasoned FPS veteran...', '<div><h2>Armedforces.io: Gear Up and Dominate!</h2><p>Armedforces.io throws you into intense firefights across diverse maps, offering a variety of game modes for every play style. Whether you\'re a seasoned FPS veteran or just starting out, this guide will provide you with the strategies and tips you need to rise through the ranks and achieve victory. Let\'s dive in!</p><h2>Understanding the Game Modes</h2><p>Armedforces.io boasts a diverse selection of game modes, each demanding a unique approach. Here\'s a breakdown:</p><ul><li><b>Team Deathmatch:</b> Classic team-based combat. Coordinate with your teammates, secure strategic points, and eliminate the opposing team to reach the score limit.</li><li><b>Free For All:</b> Every soldier for themselves! Hone your individual skills, master movement, and be the last one standing.</li><li><b>Capture the Flag:</b> A fast-paced objective-based mode. Work with your team to capture the enemy flag while defending your own. Communication and teamwork are crucial.</li></ul><h2>Mastering Movement and Gunplay</h2><p>Movement and gunplay are the cornerstones of success in Armedforces.io. Practice these techniques to gain a competitive edge:</p><ul><li><b>Strafe Jumping:</b> Combining strafing with jumps allows you to move quickly and unpredictably, making you a harder target to hit.</li><li><b>Sliding:</b> Utilize the slide mechanic to quickly close the distance, evade enemy fire, or surprise your opponents.</li><li><b>Aiming Techniques:</b> Experiment with different aiming sensitivities to find what works best for you. Practice controlling recoil and landing headshots.</li></ul><h2>Weapon Selection and Loadout Optimization</h2><p>Choosing the right weapon for the situation is crucial. Consider these factors when selecting your loadout:</p><p><b>Weapon Type:</b></p><table><tr><th>Weapon Type</th><th>Strengths</th><th>Weaknesses</th><th>Ideal Range</th></tr><tr><td>Assault Rifles</td><td>Versatile, good for medium-range engagements</td><td>Can be less effective at very long or short ranges</td><td>Medium</td></tr><tr><td>Shotguns</td><td>Devastating at close range</td><td>Ineffective at long range</td><td>Close</td></tr><tr><td>Sniper Rifles</td><td>Excellent for long-range engagements</td><td>Vulnerable in close-quarters combat</td><td>Long</td></tr><tr><td>Submachine Guns (SMGs)</td><td>High rate of fire, good for close to medium range</td><td>Less accurate than assault rifles at longer ranges</td><td>Close to Medium</td></tr></table><p><b>Attachments:</b> Equip attachments that complement your play style. Consider using sights for improved accuracy, suppressors for stealth, or extended magazines for sustained fire.</p><h2>Map Awareness and Strategic Positioning</h2><p>Knowing the maps inside and out is vital for success. Learn the key choke points, flanking routes, and power positions. Use cover effectively and anticipate enemy movements.</p><p><b>Key Strategies:</b></p><ol><li><b>Control the High Ground:</b> High ground provides a significant advantage in terms of visibility and cover.</li><li><b>Flank Your Enemies:</b> Surprise your opponents by flanking them from unexpected angles.</li><li><b>Use Grenades Strategically:</b> Grenades can be used to flush out enemies, clear objectives, or provide cover.</li></ol><h2>Teamwork and Communication</h2><p>In team-based modes, communication is essential. Use voice chat or text chat to coordinate with your teammates, call out enemy positions, and plan your attacks. Work together to achieve your objectives.</p><h2>Practice and Improvement</h2><p>The most important factor in improving your Armedforces.io skills is practice. Play regularly, experiment with different weapons and strategies, and analyze your gameplay to identify areas for improvement. Don\'t be afraid to experiment and find what works best for you.</p><h2>Conclusion: Become a Force to be Reckoned With!</h2><p>By mastering the strategies and tips outlined in this guide, you\'ll be well on your way to dominating the battlefield in Armedforces.io. Remember to practice, adapt, and most importantly, have fun! Now get out there and show them what you\'ve got!</p></div>', 'https://i.ytimg.com/vi/QgiZ1pItdqY/hq720.jpg?sqp=-oaymwEhCK4FEIIDSFryq4qpAxMIARUAAAAAGAElAADIQj0AgKJD&rs=AOn4CLDacNbRIr4uxjDc_T0mSMXWGE2ibw', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=wN8nzo__M6g', 'wN8nzo__M6g', 0, 2, 1, 'published', 'Armedforces.io Domination: The Ultimate Guide to Victory!', 'Chia sẻ mẹo và hướng dẫn chơi Armedforces.Io chi tiết nhất.', 'Armedforces.io, FPS, Gaming Guide, Shooter, Online Game', '2025-10-22 16:12:03', '2025-10-22 09:12:03', '2025-10-22 09:12:03'),
(12, 0, 'Baku The Counterpart: Mastering the Maze - A Complete Guide to Puzzle Domination', 'baku-the-counterpart-mastering-the-maze-a-complete-guide-to-puzzle-domination', 'baku-the-counterpart', '\nIntroduction: Welcome to the World of Baku The Counterpart\nBaku The Counterpart presents a deceptively simple premise: guide two Baku (creatures) to their respective goals while avoiding perilous hol...', '<div>\n<h2>Introduction: Welcome to the World of Baku The Counterpart</h2>\n<p><em>Baku The Counterpart</em> presents a deceptively simple premise: guide two Baku (creatures) to their respective goals while avoiding perilous holes. But don\'t let the initial simplicity fool you! This puzzle game rapidly evolves into a brain-bending challenge requiring careful planning, spatial reasoning, and a dash of strategic thinking. This guide will provide you with the tools and techniques necessary to conquer even the trickiest levels.</p>\n\n<h2>Understanding the Core Mechanics</h2>\n<p>At its heart, <em>Baku The Counterpart</em> revolves around simultaneous movement. Both Baku move in unison, mirroring each other\'s actions. This seemingly minor detail introduces a layer of complexity that demands meticulous planning. Here\'s a breakdown of key mechanics:</p>\n<ul>\n  <li><strong>Simultaneous Movement:</strong> Both Baku move in the same direction at the same time.</li>\n  <li><strong>Hole Avoidance:</strong> Contact with a hole results in failure, forcing a restart.</li>\n  <li><strong>Goal Orientation:</strong> Each Baku has a designated goal. Reaching both goals simultaneously is the ultimate objective.</li>\n  <li><strong>Level Design:</strong> Levels often feature narrow pathways, obstacles, and interconnected areas, requiring careful pathfinding.</li>\n</ul>\n\n<h2>Essential Strategies for Success</h2>\n<p>Mastering <em>Baku The Counterpart</em> requires more than just intuition. Here are some proven strategies to help you solve even the most challenging puzzles:</p>\n\n<h3>Visualization and Planning</h3>\n<p>Before making any moves, take a moment to visualize the entire level and potential paths for both Baku. Consider how their movements will interact and identify any potential hazards.</p>\n\n<h3>The \"Mirror Image\" Approach</h3>\n<p>Constantly be aware of the \"mirror image\" effect of your actions. If one Baku is close to a hole on the left, the other Baku is similarly vulnerable on the right. Adjust your movements accordingly.</p>\n\n<h3>Strategic Sacrifice (Sometimes)</h3>\n<p>In some levels, a temporary \"sacrifice\" – positioning one Baku precariously close to a hole – might be necessary to enable the other Baku to reach its goal. This requires careful calculation and risk assessment.</p>\n\n<h3>Experimentation is Key</h3>\n<p>Don\'t be afraid to experiment! Try different movement combinations and observe the results. Even failed attempts can provide valuable insights into the level\'s layout and potential solutions.</p>\n\n<h3>Level Specific Strategies</h3>\n<p>While general strategies are helpful, some levels demand unique approaches. Look for patterns, exploit specific level features, and don\'t be afraid to think outside the box.</p>\n\n<h2>Advanced Techniques: Thinking Ahead</h2>\n<p>Once you\'ve mastered the basics, it\'s time to delve into advanced techniques. This involves anticipating future movements and planning several steps ahead.</p>\n<ul>\n    <li><strong>Path Optimization:</strong> Identify the shortest and safest paths for both Baku.</li>\n    <li><strong>Chokepoint Navigation:</strong> Carefully navigate narrow passages where mistakes are costly.</li>\n    <li><strong>Goal Proximity Awareness:</strong> Maintain awareness of the distance to both goals and adjust your strategy accordingly.</li>\n</ul>\n\n<h2>Troubleshooting Common Problems</h2>\n<p>Stuck on a particular level? Here are some common problems and potential solutions:</p>\n<table>\n  <thead>\n    <tr>\n      <th>Problem</th>\n      <th>Possible Solution</th>\n    </tr>\n  </thead>\n  <tbody>\n    <tr>\n      <td>One Baku keeps falling into a hole.</td>\n      <td>Re-evaluate your starting position and initial movements. Are you overlooking a safer alternative path?</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td>You\'re running out of space to maneuver.</td>\n      <td>Try a different movement sequence. Experiment with small, incremental adjustments.</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td>You can\'t seem to reach both goals simultaneously.</td>\n      <td>Focus on positioning both Baku in proximity to their respective goals before making the final move.</td>\n    </tr>\n  </tbody>\n</table>\n\n<h2>Conclusion: Becoming a Baku Master</h2>\n<p><em>Baku The Counterpart</em> is a challenging but rewarding puzzle game that tests your spatial reasoning and strategic thinking. By understanding the core mechanics, applying the strategies outlined in this guide, and practicing diligently, you\'ll be well on your way to mastering the maze and achieving puzzle domination. Good luck, and have fun!</p>\n</div>', 'https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/the-witcher-fanon/images/f/fd/Putnam_Pitch_%28_Circa%2C_1490_%29.png/revision/latest?cb=20230817123535', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=upKAeWeB9Rk', 'upKAeWeB9Rk', 0, 1, 2, 'published', 'Baku The Counterpart: Mastering the Maze - A Complete Guide to Puzzle Domination', 'Chia sẻ mẹo và hướng dẫn chơi Baku The Counterpart chi tiết nhất.', 'Baku The Counterpart, Puzzle Game, Walkthrough, Strategy Guide, Tips and Tricks', '2025-10-22 16:12:44', '2025-10-22 09:12:44', '2025-10-22 09:12:44');
